# This  should  be  a  somewhat  complete  list  of  people  who  have
# contributed to  Neverball.  The  format is  copied from  the AUTHORS
# file in the XMMS2 source tree, where  in turn it was copied from the
# CREDITS file  in the  Linux kernel source  tree...  The  fields are:
# name (N), e-mail  (E), website (W), PGP key ID  and fingerprint (P),
# description (D).
#
